// ROLE:
// Deterministic divergence inspection + replay diff engine.
//
// PURPOSE:
// 1. Compare two failed replay traces.
// 2. Locate first divergence tick.
// 3. Identify first mismatched memory byte.
// 4. Print bit-level forensic diff.
// 5. Generate canonical divergence report.
